profile:
JCartwright Construction Inc. offers a full range of Commercial, Residential and Exterior Construction Services.

With a reputation for Quality and Professionalism, we will deliver your Project on Time and on Budget.

JCartwright Construction Inc. carries full WSIB Coverage and Liability Insurance for all Employees and Sub-trades.

 With over 20 years of Experience in Construction.

profile: Malcolm Millwork is a new company serving Durham and Kawartha Lakes regions. We happily provide custom cabinetry for your kitchen, bathroom, and home office. We also offer outdoor construction services such as sheds and raised garden beds. Other services include refacing/refinishing existing cabinetry as well as paint and drywalling.
